  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContextEnabled, Mojo

    @Mojo(name="generate-doc-apt",
      defaultPhase=PROCESS_SOURCES)
 @Execute(goal="generate-doc-apt",
         phase=PROCESS_SOURCES)
public class GenerateAPTDocMojo
extends AbstractDocMojo

    This goal generates an APT documentation file from TIBCO BusinessWorks source files.

    The "generate-doc-xml" goal is used to generate XML files.

    Author:
    Radwane Mabchour

        public void execute()

        Description copied from class: AbstractBWMojo

        The execute method of this Mojo will :

        • check that the BusinessWorks project exists
        • copy the Designer5.prefs file
        • copy the .designtimelibs file useful for setting a TIBCO environment for the project being built.
